{
  "stem": "21626.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they are here to this day, where we-- most of us had lost all our families, and we are each other's families.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was a wonderful blessing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the more people I talk to who came on Kindertransports and were orphaned, the more I realize how lucky I was and what my sister actually missed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she realized it when she joined me there on a few occasions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She wished she could have gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But by then she was too old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she was that much older.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And again, she, she read and wrote, you know, her diaries, and wrote to me always in Czech.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's not as perfect as mine, because I had Czech education also after the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it's, it's pretty good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she became very religious, and not in a Jewish way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, she had to go again to, to church, you know, with the school and with the families.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you see, what happened-- and again, I've learned this from lots of the children, like my best friend in Prague-- went to a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] first, a very devout Christian family.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And her older sister, who was even older than my sister, managed to get her away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then she ended up with a very highly Orthodox family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and she hated that equally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Both were very foreign to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But she said the one thing she didn't mind was going to synagogue or church because she felt her parents needed help.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the only way she could help them was by praying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And again, like me, it didn't matter where she prayed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the more she prayed, the more likely she would be to help.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And one can understand this type of a feeling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
